name: Deploy to GitHub Pages

# DISABLED
#
# This toolkit repository does not own the GitHub Pages publication target.
# The TIB/W3ID production namespace is published from TIBHannover/datacite,
# which serves https://tibhannover.github.io/datacite/ from its main branch.
#
# Keeping this file disabled prevents actions/configure-pages from failing
# with "Get Pages site failed" when GitHub Pages is not enabled for
# TIBHannover/datacite-metadata-toolkit.
#
# The active check in this repository is check-production-namespace.yml.
# Publication sync should be initiated from TIBHannover/datacite, where the
# repository-scoped GITHUB_TOKEN can open a PR against that same repository
# without requiring a cross-repository PUBLICATION_SYNC_TOKEN.
